CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: The ETFS Bloomberg Agriculture Commodity Strategy K-1 Free ETF (the Fund) is an actively managed exchange traded fund that seeks to provide a total return designed to exceed the performance of the Bloomberg Agriculture Index which is calculated on an excess return basis (the index).` The Fund is an actively managed exchange traded fund that seeks to provide a total return designed to exceed the performance of the Index. The Fund is not an index tracking exchange traded fund and is not required to invest in all components of the Index. However, the Fund will generally seek to hold similar interests to those included in the Index and will seek exposure to many of the commodities included in the Index under the same futures rolling schedule as the Index.
